content: Thank you for letting me know. What’s at the forefront of your mind right now?
“You appear to be carrying a lot right now. Let’s take it one thing at a time. What feels most important to share?”
It seems like something’s stirring for you. Let’s give it space—what do you notice?
“It seems like you’re holding a lot of uncertainty right now. Where do you feel that most in your life?”
It seems like relationships are on your mind. What’s most present for you when you think about them right now?
